verses.text: Unto \w the|strong="H0623"\w* end, for \w the|strong="H0623"\w* winepresses, a \w psalm|strong="H4210"\w* for \w the|strong="H0623"\w* sons of Core.
How lovely \w are|strong="H0430"\w* thy tabernacles, \w O|strong="H0430"\w* Lord \w of|strong="H0430"\w* host!

\w My|strong="H3588"\w* soul longeth \w and|strong="H7218"\w* fainteth \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* courts \w of|strong="H7218"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* Lord. \w My|strong="H3588"\w* heart \w and|strong="H7218"\w* \w my|strong="H3588"\w* flesh \w have|strong="H3588"\w* rejoiced \w in|strong="H7218"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* living God.

\w For|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* sparrow hath found \w herself|strong="H5921"\w* \w a|strong="H5921"\w* house, \w and|strong="H3289"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* turtle \w a|strong="H5921"\w* nest \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w herself|strong="H5921"\w* \w where|strong="H5921"\w* she may lay \w her|strong="H5921"\w* young ones: Thy altars, O Lord \w of|strong="H5921"\w* hosts, \w my|strong="H5921"\w* \w king|strong="H5921"\w* \w and|strong="H3289"\w* \w my|strong="H5921"\w* God.

Blessed \w are|strong="H3478"\w* \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w that|strong="H0559"\w* dwell \w in|strong="H3478"\w* thy house, \w O|strong="H2142"\w* Lord: \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w shall|strong="H3478"\w* praise thee \w for|strong="H3808"\w* \w ever|strong="H5750"\w* \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w ever|strong="H5750"\w*.

Blessed \w is|strong="H3820"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* man whose help \w is|strong="H3820"\w* \w from|strong="H5921"\w* thee: \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w his|strong="H5921"\w* \w heart|strong="H3820"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* hath disposed \w to|strong="H5921"\w* ascend \w by|strong="H5921"\w* steps,
In the vale \w of|strong="H0168"\w* tears, in the place which be hath set.

\w For|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H5973"\w* lawgiver \w shall|strong="H3427"\w* give \w a|strong="H3427"\w* blessing, \w they|strong="H5983"\w* \w shall|strong="H3427"\w* go \w from|strong="H5973"\w* virtue \w to|strong="H5973"\w* virtue: \w the|strong="H5973"\w* God \w of|strong="H3427"\w* gods \w shall|strong="H3427"\w* be seen \w in|strong="H3427"\w* Sion.
O Lord God \w of|strong="H1121"\w* hosts, hear \w my|strong="H1961"\w* prayer: \w give|strong="H1961"\w* ear, O God \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Jacob.
Behold, O God our protector: \w and|strong="H4080"\w* look on \w the|strong="H6213"\w* face of thy Christ.

\w For|strong="H0127"\w* better \w is|strong="H1961"\w* \w one|strong="H1961"\w* day \w in|strong="H1961"\w* thy courts above thousands. \w I|strong="H1961"\w* \w have|strong="H1961"\w* chosen \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \w an|strong="H1961"\w* abject \w in|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H1961"\w* house \w of|strong="H0127"\w* \w my|strong="H1961"\w* God, rather than \w to|strong="H1961"\w* dwell \w in|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H1961"\w* tabernacles \w of|strong="H0127"\w* sinners.
\w For|strong="H3605"\w* God loveth mercy \w and|strong="H2078"\w* truth: \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Lord \w will|strong="H3605"\w* give grace \w and|strong="H2078"\w* glory.

\w He|strong="H0834"\w* \w will|strong="H0430"\w* not deprive \w of|strong="H0430"\w* good \w things|strong="H0834"\w* \w them|strong="H0853"\w* \w that|strong="H0834"\w* walk \w in|strong="H0430"\w* innocence: \w O|strong="H0430"\w* Lord \w of|strong="H0430"\w* hosts, blessed \w is|strong="H0834"\w* \w the|strong="H0853"\w* man \w that|strong="H0834"\w* trusteth \w in|strong="H0430"\w* thee.
